snippet.title: Star Conflict - Official Teaser
snippet.description:
Developer - Star Gem
Publisher - Gaijin Entertainment

Star Conflict is a new dynamic multiplayer online action game that puts you at the helm of a space ship to fight in the star fleet's massive battles!

Official website: http://star-conflict.com
Forum : http://forum.star-conflict.com/
